MG_RUINZTRAP_COURSE_V3

THIS IS NORMAL VERSION

|||LINK HARDCORE [mg_ruinztrap_course_hc_v1] |||

New killing course with unique style, traps, music, secrets, etc...

Features:
- Unique style
- Unique traps
- Spawnkill in 40 seconds
- 64 slots
- NavFile
- AutoRespawnPlugin (if available)
- Grenades (new style trails)
- Grenades (secrets\speed)
- 3 challenges:
   - Main challenge - 100 points
   - Bonus1 (elevator) challenge - 100 points
   - Bonus2 (slide) challenge - 100 points
- Excellent background music at all challenges (+1)
- Some custom textures

requires noblock plugin
